OL,6,FHe told UTV "the increase will be
OL,7,Fdrastic, it equates to #800,000 a
OL,8,Fyear, in other words that is #15,500
OL,9,Fper week.
OL,11,F"We are trying to make sure we even
OL,12,Fout our staff as best as possible and
OL,13,Fmake sure they work at the right time.
OL,14,FWe also have a moratorium on bringing
OL,15,Fin new people"
OL,17,F"It is very difficult to deal with
OL,18,Fbecause we are at the end of the
OL,19,Fsupply chain."
